column1: It seems that the people in Gensokyo are not your ordinary folks.
All right, now you need to fulfill our promise,
and take me to visit the Outside World, OK?
Erm… Are you really serious in going?
I’m sure the Outside world have lots of meaningful things going around right?
When I return home, I will tell lots of stories to my elder sister!
Well then, let’s go get you a change of clothes first.
This is to prevent any unnecessary trouble during our stay in the Outside world.
I wonder how will it looks like? I am curious!
Well then, during our visit in the Outside World, you will need to obey me, OK?
Don’t run around all over the place, OK?
